messageBody:
Hello. I just uploaded some more files to my intQS project:
prepositions, conjunctions and the hardbasket.
All files already existing have been updated with bug fixes as well.
A major change in the proposal is that I have now broken the happY set
into two- 1)an untensed set- rabbIt and 2)a tensed set happY. See the
Notes_and_Info file for more details if interested.
